description:
This is a 15 minute workout called 'Intense Interval Blast | 15 Minute Indoor Cycling Workout' from the channel GCN Training.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor biking and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Firestarter and The Adrenaline Rush vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Get your legs spinning (and burning) with these 30-second sprints! Hank guides you through two main sets of intervals: one gentler, and the other pushing you to work at your limits! Get ready to sweat!
